{"tid":637789,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★[回帶]華為CEO：過了34歲就是廢人！華為裁走34歲以上IT狗！","createTime":"2018-04-22T06:55:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-22T08:32:29.000Z","uid":19454,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"ae164157e27b366f7014e86fa1778e9ee73c64db","tid":637789,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T06:55:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">華為興衰在此一舉 任正非：過了34歲就是廢人</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n華為公司被爆出辭退34歲以上程式員的消息，這些程式員都已經為公司工作了十多年。展程CEO陳羽翔被指獨吞股權，逼走一起創業七年的程式員伙伴，從時間上來算創業七年也恰巧是30多歲的年紀。任正非解釋道：30多歲的程式員不能熬夜，失去激情30多歲的程式員成本太高，性價比太低，30多歲的程式員在法律上有更多權利。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.haixiaba.com/n369413.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.haixiaba.com%2Fn369413.html&d=0HwJE49gAfonorBSzpbb2e9M5Ue6CDmcYDZznX2R1Ws%3D&h=011f8eb6\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.haixiaba.com/n369413.html</a>"},{"pid":"351c5d07b434f2f7633874ef844c7cd296ff91b2","tid":637789,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T06:56:24.000Z","msg":"對華為來說，已經是一個油盡燈枯的廢物，除了耗費公司資源，已經不能給公司帶來利潤和活力了。網上載有員工34歲要退休，不知誰來給他們支付退休金？難道在任正非眼里30幾歲的人就這么不堪嗎？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.mp.itc.cn/upload/20170226/b205401881c9475f917f2f37ebd636ed.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.mp.itc.cn%2Fupload%2F20170226%2Fb205401881c9475f917f2f37ebd636ed.jpg&h=62a87d7c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e75ad02dbff42ef0f8f2ae5f354a2fd1dfe8eb17","tid":637789,"uid":38554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T06:57:38.000Z","msg":"34同35有咩唔同"},{"pid":"bf0bcae0a68ba796f47fae1c32f219c81acc381f","tid":637789,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e75ad02dbff42ef0f8f2ae5f354a2fd1dfe8eb17","tid":637789,"uid":38554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T06:57:38.000Z","msg":"34同35有咩唔同"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T06:58:58.000Z","msg":"踏入更年期？"},{"pid":"a812ee8f7818b69da6881